Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.21,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319172,1321216}{\i1}Tomorrow is my Mom's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:04.67,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321216,1324678}{\i1}But looks like Dad lost his salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:07.80,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324678,1327806}{\i1}He can't buy any gift for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.97,lassie default,John Carraclough,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327806,1330976}{\i1}Lassie, we're gonna\Nlook for it with your nose!
